  "name": "Plasma Snuff",
  "type": "consumable",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "folder": "fhSubSciFi000001",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cool blue dust harvested from spent reactor scrubbers and cut with finer commercial stims. The first hit makes the world hum at the rate of a passing dropship. Track-runners take it before a sprint; mechanics take it before a 24-hour shift.</p><p><strong><em>Desired effects on use.</em></strong> For 1 hour your walking speed increases by 10 feet and you have advantage on Dexterity saving throws.</p><p><strong><em>On use, save against addiction.</em></strong> Make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, you gain the Addicted condition from Plasma Snuff (see below).</p><p><strong><em>Addicted from Plasma Snuff.</em></strong> While you have this Addicted condition, you are also Poisoned and have disadvantage on Wisdom saving throws (your attention skitters from one thing to the next).</p><p><strong><em>Withdrawal Modifier: 3.</em></strong> Withdrawal lasts max(3 &minus; your Constitution modifier, 2) long rests, minimum 1.</p><p><em>Requires: Snuff Horn.</em></p>"
    },
